{"tid":750644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"易志明促同罰白牌車  ︰白牌車時間彈性、有兩三萬收入，咁年輕司機就唔打工","createTime":"2018-07-21T05:34:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-21T16:04:55.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"26b92e009a93d629fb7296806e447ef196f5c5db","tid":750644,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180721/s00001/49795597e4a1aa0fec1a36ec4d538a4b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180721%2Fs00001%2F49795597e4a1aa0fec1a36ec4d538a4b.jpg&h=c142eb51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n的士濫收車資及兜路、拒載等問題向來為人詬病，政府日前向立法會提交文件，建議引入的士司機扣分制，將11項罪行納入扣分項目。立法會交通事務委員會主席易志明認為，如果的士引入扣分罰則，應該同樣引入對白牌車的罰則，不要令的士司機覺得政府針對合規經營之的士。<br />\n<br />\n本身屬於航運交通界別的易志明今早在商台節目上表示，白牌車不單影響的士生意，還令運輸業界找不到司機。他說，的士業司機不足，導致老闆要繼續租車給有問題的司機，否則沒有租金。<br />\n<br />\n易志明說，現在有「兩蚊司機」及「生果金司機」兩個新名稱，即65歲的司機及70歲或以上的司機，但這情況不理想，因為長者不多不少會有長期疾病，成了道路計時炸彈，對路上安全不好。<br />\n<br />\n易志明認為，很多年輕司機選擇駕駛白牌車，因為成本低、時間彈性、不用受老闆氣，「包你有兩萬幾三萬收入，那麼他們就不選擇打工」。他認為加強打擊白牌車，一定可以讓大量司機退回來。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，近年客貨車突然增多，根本是在做非法載客取酬的生意，他建議取消客貨車中間一行的座位，「就不會去載客，(是)很簡單的事」。他認為，司機旁兩個座位已經足夠，質疑貨客車中間為什麼要有座位。<br />\n<br />\n同場的立法會議員尹兆堅聞言即表示，貨車要有「跟車」幫忙搬貨，但易志明反駁說根本沒有那人跟車，現時多數只有一個跟車。易志明又說，明白有些行業有特別情況，他們可另行向運輸署申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180721/s00001/1532138616111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180721%2Fs00001%2F1532138616111&d=CO2bB9pivYlzsX4o0%2BYAkZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=32af00a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180721%2Fs00001%2F1532138616111&h=1082676a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180721/s00001/1532138616111</a>"},{"pid":"2945159c2121b7385875180572884175aaf33be6","tid":750644,"uid":62532,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:37:13.000Z","msg":"自己做到生意點解要打工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6bc8dc9b61d1034032812743fd8460b9254847","tid":750644,"uid":36054,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"咁癲既野都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea85acdcfa621921ceb6a1af11df19da5fa0d5a","tid":750644,"uid":85629,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:37:50.000Z","msg":"正宗土皇帝思維：個個都要為我打工、為我奴隷"},{"pid":"a216ec25baaca2f4072c9549730a6ba14bde3f1a","tid":750644,"uid":40340,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:40:56.000Z","msg":"建議將白牌車5成收入分返比的士狗<br />\n再每日幫佢地洗車"},{"pid":"66efe7457b4616299f2e395948b37d0b9c437891","tid":750644,"uid":4661,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:45:39.000Z","msg":"唔打工都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d304383ef70adad5377600cdc3d93bf5a3e1b88","tid":750644,"uid":53687,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:49:59.000Z","msg":"易志明：你唔幫我打工，我嘛要自己搵工，咁我邊有時間發UP瘋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2fd5cfbb44e8166223de506efef92f2a5b16979","tid":750644,"uid":8880,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:50:34.000Z","msg":"講咗腦細d心底話出嚟 佢好撚驚真係有白牌車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76be861de98bbca353601aefaa5b15d2dfee688f","tid":750644,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:53:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"990065ed4bd5215f14859a7947def5fe856bfd57","tid":750644,"uid":44486,"like":7,"dislike":0,"sc